LTC2947-65: high-precision power and energy monitor with an internal sense resistor supporting up to 65A.

NOTE:
The DC2574A-KIT includes the following items:
- DC2334A: LTC2947-65 Demo Circuit
- DC2026: Linduino with Pre-Programmed "LTC2947 - DC2574B_KIT Linduino.INO File" (THIS FILE!)
